firmwareguard (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Complete Phase 1 & 2 implementation
  * Hardware probe engine (MSR, PCI, MMIO)
  * Intel ME and AMD PSP detection
  * ACPI table parsing for telemetry
  * NIC firmware telemetry detection
  * Active blocking and mitigation
  * Pattern-based detection database
  * Offline-only architecture
  * Security hardening (stack protection, PIE, RELRO)
  * Safety framework with backups and rollback
  * Systemd service integration
  * Comprehensive documentation

 -- FirmwareGuard Team <contact@firmwareguard.dev>  Fri, 29 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000
